 subsequent to the installing of the firmware image, receiving a plugin application, wherein the plugin application is configured to perform thermal management of at least one unsupported card inserted in the information handling system; 
 cryptographically verifying a source of the plugin application; 
 installing the plugin application onto the storage resource; and 
 executing the plugin application.

